N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15 ยง 5.6 - Renewal of licenses

State Regulations

The license of a person who is required to submit to a
vision reexamination will not be renewed until satisfactory evidence of meeting
the minimum vision requirements is submitted as required by this
